<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 14:03:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“感觉像大屠杀”：惊恐的以色列人讲述哈马斯突然入侵后的恐怖行为</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/felt-like-holocaust-terrified-israelis-recount-hamas-terror-after-surprise-invasion/articleshow/104261870.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104261870.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列面临数十年来最大规模的入侵，民众在持续不断的暴力事件中躲进防空洞避难。哈马斯恐怖分子袭击和暴行的视频在社交媒体上流传，描绘了一幅严峻的局势。以色列记者夫妇哈纳尼亚（Hananya）和印度纳夫塔利（India Naftali）分享了他们在特拉维夫因火箭爆炸而醒来的经历。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:37:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/felt-like-holocaust-terrified-israelis-recount-hamas-terror-after-surprise-invasion/articleshow/104261870.cms</guid></item><item><title>在以色列和加沙的印度国民安全</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/indian-nationals-in-israel-and-gaza-safe/articleshow/104260605.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104260605.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在以色列紧张局势不断升级的情况下，迄今为止尚未有涉及在该国生活和工作的印度人发生不幸事件的报道。印度驻特拉维夫大使馆已收到包括游客在内的滞留印度公民的请求，要求他们安全出境。使馆一直积极指导和帮助印度公民，建议他们保持警惕并遵守安全规定。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 11:06:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/indian-nationals-in-israel-and-gaza-safe/articleshow/104260605.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰总统：中东暴力有利于俄罗斯，增加了欧盟的移民压力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/mideast-violence-benefits-russia-adds-to-migration-pressure-on-eu-polish-president/articleshow/104260219.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104260219.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰总统安杰伊·杜达表示，哈马斯和以色列之间持续的暴力活动转移了国际社会对其侵略乌克兰的注意力，这对俄罗斯有利。杜达还担心冲突可能导致欧洲移民压力增加，特别是来自中东的移民压力。波兰一直是乌克兰的支持者，并庇护了超过一百万乌克兰难民。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 10:45:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/mideast-violence-benefits-russia-adds-to-migration-pressure-on-eu-polish-president/articleshow/104260219.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国最高法院权衡英国将寻求庇护者送往卢旺达是否合法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-supreme-court-weighs-if-its-lawful-for-britain-to-send-asylum-seekers-to-rwanda/articleshow/104262509.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104262509.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国政府有争议的阻止移民流动的政策本周面临最严峻的挑战之一，英国最高法院正在权衡将寻求庇护者送往卢旺达是否合法。保守党政府正在对上诉法院六月份的一项裁决提出质疑，该裁决称，旨在阻止移民冒着生命危险乘小船穿越英吉利海峡的政策是非法的，因为这个东非国家不是一个安全的移民目的地。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 13:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-supreme-court-weighs-if-its-lawful-for-britain-to-send-asylum-seekers-to-rwanda/articleshow/104262509.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登谴责哈马斯的“令人震惊的袭击”，以色列盟友表达愤怒和震惊</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-condemns-the-appalling-assault-by-hamas-as-israels-allies-express-anger-and-shock/articleshow/104258943.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104258943.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总统乔·拜登谴责哈马斯武装分子对以色列的袭击，并承诺支持确保以色列的防御。国务卿安东尼·布林肯和国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀正在与外国同行举行会议和通话。美国打算与该地区的阿拉伯伙伴合作缓和局势，但预计不会出现短期解决方案。世界领导人对以色列自卫权表示声援。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 09:32:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-condemns-the-appalling-assault-by-hamas-as-israels-allies-express-anger-and-shock/articleshow/104258943.cms</guid></item><item><title>用战斧砸碎国会大厦窗户的骚乱者被判入狱7年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/capitol-rioter-who-smashed-windows-with-tomahawk-axe-jailed-for-7-years/articleshow/104259006.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104259006.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;参与 1 月 6 日国会大厦骚乱的唐纳德·特朗普支持者肖恩·詹金斯 (Shane Jenkins) 被判处七年联邦监狱监禁。詹金斯被称为“骷髅”，他砸碎了一扇窗户，向警察投掷弹丸，并被判犯有九项刑事罪名。政府寻求判处 19 年以上徒刑，但詹金斯的律师辩称他受到了有关选举的虚假说法的影响。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 09:38:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/capitol-rioter-who-smashed-windows-with-tomahawk-axe-jailed-for-7-years/articleshow/104259006.cms</guid></item><item><title>2024 年美国大选：小罗伯特·肯尼迪是否会放弃民主党并以独立人士身份参选？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-election-2024-is-rfk-jr-going-to-ditch-the-democratic-party-and-run-as-an-independent/articleshow/104258749.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104258749.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪(Robert F. Kennedy Jr.)即将宣布退出民主党，并针对乔·拜登(JoeBiden)发起独立总统竞选。肯尼迪指责民主党官员密谋反对他，导致他决定退党。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 09:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-election-2024-is-rfk-jr-going-to-ditch-the-democratic-party-and-run-as-an-independent/articleshow/104258749.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构呼吁召开阿拉伯联盟紧急会议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-authority-calls-for-emergency-arab-league-meeting/articleshow/104258554.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104258554.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 09:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinian-authority-calls-for-emergency-arab-league-meeting/articleshow/104258554.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本计划于12月举行东盟和澳大利亚脱碳峰会：共同社</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-plans-to-hold-asean-australia-summit-on-decarbonisation-in-dec-kyodo/articleshow/104257950.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104257950.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:41:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japan-plans-to-hold-asean-australia-summit-on-decarbonisation-in-dec-kyodo/articleshow/104257950.cms</guid></item><item><title>世界对哈马斯袭击以色列做出反应</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-reacts-to-hamas-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104257761.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104257761.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯对以色列发动大规模袭击，引发世界各地的反应。美国谴责恐怖主义并对以色列表示声援。联合国呼吁缓和局势，伊朗则赞扬巴勒斯坦武装分子。中国敦促克制，并强调两国解决方案的必要性。欧洲领导人谴责袭击事件并支持以色列自卫权利。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:31:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-reacts-to-hamas-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104257761.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌干达黑猩猩抢走婴儿迫使家庭放弃家园</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/baby-snatching-chimpanzees-in-uganda-force-families-to-abandon-homes/articleshow/104261718.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104261718.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于自然栖息地的丧失，乌干达农村地区的黑猩猩越来越多地侵入人类社区，导致儿童与母亲失散的令人痛苦的事件。珍·古道尔研究所估计，乌干达栖息着大约 5,000 只黑猩猩，虽然袭击人类的情况很少见，但它们促使人们需要找到解决方案来解决不断升级的冲突。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:19:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/baby-snatching-chimpanzees-in-uganda-force-families-to-abandon-homes/articleshow/104261718.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国警方在伦敦与以色列冲突有关的事件中加强巡逻</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-police-increase-patrols-amid-incidents-in-london-related-to-israel-conflict/articleshow/104257852.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104257852.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在一系列与以色列冲突有关的事件发生后，苏格兰场增加了伦敦各地的巡逻。伦敦警察厅正在对社交媒体上分享的消息和图像做出回应。英国内政部部长罗伯特·詹里克谴责哈马斯美化恐怖活动，伦敦市长萨迪克·汗警告称，不会容忍仇恨犯罪。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-police-increase-patrols-amid-incidents-in-london-related-to-israel-conflict/articleshow/104257852.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列称24小时内撤离加沙附近居民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-to-evacuate-residents-near-gaza-within-24-hours/articleshow/104257542.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104257542.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-to-evacuate-residents-near-gaza-within-24-hours/articleshow/104257542.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙与以色列的战争死亡人数上升至313人：外交部</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-death-toll-in-war-with-israel-rises-to-313-ministry/articleshow/104257120.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104257120.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 07:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-death-toll-in-war-with-israel-rises-to-313-ministry/articleshow/104257120.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯暴力迫使沙特与以色列的势头绕道</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-violently-forces-detour-from-saudi-israel-momentum/articleshow/104255616.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104255616.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯对以色列的突然袭击对确保美国斡旋的以色列和沙特阿拉伯之间达成协议的努力造成了打击。这次袭击将世界的注意力重新转移到巴勒斯坦问题上，使其更难以被忽视。总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡曾希望得到沙特阿拉伯的承认，但暴力事件使正常化谈判变得复杂。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-violently-forces-detour-from-saudi-israel-momentum/articleshow/104255616.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们正处于战争之中”：关于哈马斯激进组织对以色列史无前例的袭击，您需要了解的五件事</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/we-are-at-war-5-things-to-know-about-the-hamas-militant-groups-unprecedented-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104255856.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104255856.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙的哈马斯统治者利用空中、陆地和海上对以色列发动了突然袭击。这次袭击包括火箭弹，炸毁了以色列部分隔离栅栏，并渗透到加沙边境沿线的以色列社区。这次袭击让以色列措手不及，引发了有关情报失误的质疑。哈马斯声称俘虏了以色列人，并发布了视频来支持他们的说法。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/we-are-at-war-5-things-to-know-about-the-hamas-militant-groups-unprecedented-attack-on-israel/articleshow/104255856.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟地中海部长呼吁遣返更多移民并增加资源</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-mediterranean-ministers-call-for-more-migrant-repatriations-and-increased-resources/articleshow/104255700.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104255700.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;来自塞浦路斯、希腊、意大利、马耳他和西班牙的移民和内政部长赞扬了欧盟新的移民协议，但呼吁提供更多资源。这些被称为地中海五国集团的部长们对非法进入欧盟的回国移民采取了强硬立场，并警告说，如果不果断解决这个问题，极端的声音可能会产生影响。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-mediterranean-ministers-call-for-more-migrant-repatriations-and-increased-resources/articleshow/104255700.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度裔女孩将参加奥地利世界青少年台球锦标赛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/indian-origin-girl-to-compete-in-austrias-world-junior-billiards-championship/articleshow/104255466.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104255466.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 9 岁的印度裔台球神童 Tanvee Vallem 在奥地利著名的 Predator WPA 世界 10 球青少年锦标赛中赢得了一席之地。比赛将于 10 月 19 日至 22 日举行，采用 10 球赛制，反映了这项运动不断变化的趋势。坦维来自海得拉巴，居住在马里兰州，他作为波多黎各 Predator 世界青少年 9 球锦标赛最年轻的参赛者创造了历史。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/nri/indian-origin-girl-to-compete-in-austrias-world-junior-billiards-championship/articleshow/104255466.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在突袭第二天与哈马斯交火，真主党和以色列交火</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-and-israel-exchange-fire-as-israeli-soldiers-battle-hamas-on-second-day-of-surprise-attack/articleshow/104255415.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104255415.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列士兵与哈马斯武装分子发生冲突，并与真主党交火，引发了人们对更广泛地区冲突的担忧。战斗发生之前，巴勒斯坦武装分子对以色列南部发动突然袭击，造成至少 250 人死亡。哈马斯武装分子冲出加沙地带，劫持俘虏并向以色列城市发射火箭弹。以色列通过袭击加沙目标进行报复。真主党还袭击了与叙利亚戈兰高地接壤的以色列阵地。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:12:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-and-israel-exchange-fire-as-israeli-soldiers-battle-hamas-on-second-day-of-surprise-attack/articleshow/104255415.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿塞拜疆总统表示，如果与亚美尼亚爆发新冲突，法国将承担责任</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/azerbaijans-president-says-france-will-be-to-blame-if-new-conflict-starts-with-armenia/articleshow/104255293.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104255293.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿塞拜疆总统伊利哈姆·阿利耶夫批评欧盟，特别是法国向亚美尼亚提供军事援助，称这可能导致南高加索地区爆发新的冲突。阿利耶夫发表此番言论之前，他拒绝参加由欧盟斡旋的与亚美尼亚总理尼科尔·帕辛扬的会晤。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:05:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/azerbaijans-president-says-france-will-be-to-blame-if-new-conflict-starts-with-armenia/articleshow/104255293.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>